page.title: 05Tring to move?
page.content: Members of a Dacorum council sub committee set up to consider the issue were told that Bucks county council now included Tring town and Tring rural parish.Aldbury parish and Wigginton parish in its list of proposals to the commission. The report went before Dacorum's policy committee last week and it was agreed to restate the borough's opposition to the proposals for Tring.It is quite clear that Tring and Dacorum councils are against Tring and some other towns being put into Buckinghamshire from Hertfordshire.
